I"><h1 id="bef-is-a-responsive-jekyll-theme">Bef is a responsive jekyll theme</h1>

<p>Bef - Blog Enjoy Freedom is a responsive jekyll theme which created to
be simple and freedom.</p>

<h2 id="demo">Demo</h2>

<p>Check the theme in action <a href="https://artemsheludko.github.io/bef/">Demo</a></p>

<p>The main page would look like this:</p>

<p><img src="https://github.com/artemsheludko/bef/blob/master/assets/img/bef_main_page.jpg?raw=true" alt="Main page preview" /></p>

<p>The post page would look like this:</p>

<p><img src="https://github.com/artemsheludko/bef/blob/master/assets/img/bef_post.jpg?raw=true" alt="Post page preview" /></p>

