<ul>
  <li><a href="https://fonts.google.com/">Google Fonts</a></li>
  <li><a href="http://fontawesome.io/">Font Awesome</a></li>
  <li><a href="http://vodkabears.github.io/vide/">Vide</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://disqus.com/">Disqus</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://mailchimp.com/">MailChimp</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://formspree.io/">Formspree!</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://analytics.google.com/analytics/web/">Analytics</a></li>
  <li>Share Buttons, Recent Post, Section Author, Contact and moreâ€¦</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="installation">Installation:</h2>

<p>Fork the <code>master</code> branch and delete <code>gh-pages</code> branch in it. This
is important because <code>gh-pages</code> branch is used here only to host the
blog. You should be using the master branch as the source and create a
fresh <code>gh-pages</code> branch.</p>

